{"tid":2199043,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"以色列與巴林同意建交　巴勒斯坦稱再被阿拉伯世界捅刀","createTime":"2020-09-12T00:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T04:11:45.000Z","uid":295230,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8800e935967c3831e9a3543b807fc1086f13ae94","tid":2199043,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T00:44:39.000Z","msg":"以色列同巴林同意建立全面外交關係。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普表示，是中東和平另一個歷史性突破日子，巴林是30天內同以色列關係正常化的第二個阿拉伯國家，亦是對911事件最強力回應。<br />\n<br />\n巴勒斯坦自治組織譴責，形容是阿拉伯世界另一次背後插刀，向巴勒斯坦人侵略。控制加沙地帶的哈馬斯，是出於對巴勒斯坦人偏見造成的侵略。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n笑左，巴勒斯坦人真可愛，居然仲覺得班阿拉伯人係真心想幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5d99c3841e0de2e683f3c3b6ebe88db5c56b25","tid":2199043,"uid":4493,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T00:55:27.000Z","msg":"其實都係提示我哋<br />\n要令到西方國家覺得值得幫 香港先至有救<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a77a8a44432341efa5cd6616890cc69b074a449","tid":2199043,"uid":50386,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T01:06:59.000Z","msg":"巴勒斯坦撐得支那<br />\n就預咗會俾文明世界遺棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e4f0187c1f4f6a7f322a7a081029682ff4401f","tid":2199043,"uid":32151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"db5d99c3841e0de2e683f3c3b6ebe88db5c56b25","tid":2199043,"uid":4493,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T00:55:27.000Z","msg":"其實都係提示我哋<br />\n要令到西方國家覺得值得幫 香港先至有救<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T01:24:50.000Z","msg":"認同  美國都係照顧本土為主 所以未必幫你 無咁多大愛 <br />\n都係講求利益 但你有誘因吸引到佢 佢自然會幫你"},{"pid":"34b3bcb850ca1a770672eda12bbcbdecc987743e","tid":2199043,"uid":336583,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"3a77a8a44432341efa5cd6616890cc69b074a449","tid":2199043,"uid":50386,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"